00:27:10,341 --> 00:27:13,804
Button cardigan, I'm reserved, open,

478
00:27:13,804 --> 00:27:15,886
kind of sloppy, but don't care.

479
00:27:15,886 --> 00:27:19,150
Jeans and combers, meaning I'm ready for an adventure.

