00:27:36,291 --> 00:27:41,616
I think we got down to around 8,000 triangles for his model.

485
00:27:41,616 --> 00:27:48,942
So Lolo went through a few versions as well.

486
00:27:48,942 --> 00:27:52,885
Classic leather jacket, jean jacket, ripped jeans.

487
00:27:52,885 --> 00:27:54,847
For her hair, we really embraced the iconic,

488
00:27:54,847 --> 00:27:57,749
thick, kinky hair that subtly bounces.

